<solution>
<p><ul><li>37.6</li><li>86.1</li></ul></p><p>The perimeter is the sum of the four sides which are given. <m>\displaystyle{7.09}+{9.71}+{10.68}+{10.12}={37.6}</m>.</p>
<p>The area is given by <m>\displaystyle\frac{{1}}{{2}}{\left({a}+{b}\right)}=\frac{{1}}{{2}}{\left({7.09}+{10.68}\right)}={86.09565}\approx{86.1}</m>.</p>
</solution>
